description:

Ingredients: (makes about 12-14)

4 medium size potatoes
1 medium size sweet potato
1/2 small pumpkin
(about 1.5 kilos all up of veggies)
1 cup of peas
puff pastry
3/4 teaspoon of cumin
3/4 teaspoon of garam marsala
2 teaspoons of curry powder
title: VEGETABLE SAMOSAS: OVEN BAKED
